 considered when methotrexate is used with other potentially hepatotoxic agents (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/37846/', '', 'Tinidazole, Cefixime, Secnidazole, Rifamycin, Netilmicin, Trifluridine, Chlorhexidine, Povidone-iodine, Lincomycin, Dirithromycin', 'Golimumab, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, More', 1767369485);
